About Jumpossess
Experience Jumpossess - Master unique puzzle platforming with supernatural possession abilities. Switch between characters to solve challenging puzzles and reach your goals.

Master Jumpossess's unique gameplay mechanics and challenge yourself to new achievements.

The possession system in Jumpossess allows you to take control of different characters, each with unique abilities essential for solving puzzles.
